Package: ariadne
Version: @VERSION@
Section: editors
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCHITECTURE@
Maintainer: Ariadne contributors <https://github.com/yanshaoqwq/Ariadne>
Homepage: https://github.com/yanshaoqwq/Ariadne
Installed-Size: @INSTALLED_SIZE@
Depends: libc6, libfontconfig1, libfreetype6, libx11-6, libxrandr2, libxrender1, libxcb1
Description: AI writing workbench for long-form fiction
 Ariadne combines workflow orchestration, long-form writing, retrieval,
 knowledge management, and version history in a local-first desktop app.
